(43, 12, 38, 23, 53, 1, 1, 'Who hath believed our report?', 'Connection of Prophetic Fulfillment', 'This connection highlights the direct quotation of Isaiah 53:1 in John 12:38, emphasizing the theme of belief in the report of the Lord. Both passages ask the same rhetorical questions, linking the prophetic message to its fulfillment in the New Testament.', 'quotation', 0.5309999999999999, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
