(43, 12, 38, 46, 1, 24, 24, 'who hath believed our report?', 'Power and Belief in Christ', 'This connection highlights the theme of belief in God''s revelation. Both passages emphasize the response to God''s power, with John referencing belief in the report and Corinthians affirming Christ as the power of God.', 'theme', 0.33499999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
