(43, 12, 38, 40, 16, 17, 17, 'arm of the Lord', 'Revelation of the Father', 'This connection highlights the theme of divine revelation. In both passages, the concept of revelation is emphasized, with John referencing the ''arm of the Lord'' and Matthew noting that the Father reveals truth to Peter.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'medium', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(43, 12, 38, 44, 8, 28, 30, 'Esaias the prophet', 'Connection of Prophetic Fulfillment', 'Both passages emphasize the prophet Esaias, highlighting the theme of belief in the report of the Lord. The mention of Esaias in both contexts connects the fulfillment of prophecy with the act of understanding scripture.', 'prophecy', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
